            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>春笋上市！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%90%83%E6%98%A5%E7%AC%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%90%83%E6%98%A5%E7%AC%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些人不宜吃春笋#</span></a>？】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E7%AC%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E7%AC%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃笋要注意什么#</span></a> 春笋上市，成为很多人家中餐桌上的美食，春笋好吃有营养，但有一个缺点是不好消化。近日，江苏一<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%B4%AA%E5%90%83%E6%98%A5%E7%AC%8B%E5%90%8E%E5%91%95%E8%A1%80%E5%8F%88%E6%98%8F%E5%8E%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%B4%AA%E5%90%83%E6%98%A5%E7%AC%8B%E5%90%8E%E5%91%95%E8%A1%80%E5%8F%88%E6%98%8F%E5%8E%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#男子贪吃春笋后呕血又昏厥#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>吃笋还能吃出胃出血？专家提醒，竹笋含有大量的粗纤维以及丰富的钾元素，肝硬化患者、肾功能衰竭和血钾升高患者、胃肠道疾病患者、泌尿系统结石患者，都应减少对春笋的摄入。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6N727im" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
